
1) local -> local replication (make hardlink)
2) create pending dir
3) new attachments in pending dir, synced, write_and_commit, then moved into place.
4) deleted attachments moved to pending dir, write_and_commit, then deleted
5) pending dir scanned on db open, items deleted or moved into place as needed.
6) move _attachments/%db%/ to .delete dir on db deletion
